data.description: **STEINBRENNER DISTRICT** Welcome to 16128 Manorwood Cir, a charming home nestled in the desirable Northdale neighborhood. This delightful property offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, making it an ideal space for a variety of buyers, whether you're an investor or a first-time homebuyer.    Step inside and be greeted by a warm and inviting interior. The layout is perfect for those seeking a comfortable and functional living space. The home boasts a range of interior features, allowing you to add your personal touch and make it your own.    As you explore the exterior of the property, you'll discover a hidden gem. Situated on 1.07 acres and a canal and surrounded by beautiful conservation, this home provides a serene and peaceful atmosphere with no neighbors in the back. Imagine waking up to the tranquil sounds of nature and enjoying your morning coffee while taking in the picturesque views.    Located in the sought-after Northdale neighborhood, this property offers convenient access to a variety of amenities and attractions. Enjoy the nearby parks, shopping centers, and dining options, all just a short distance away. Whether you're looking for a day of outdoor adventure or a night out on the town, this location has it all. Bring your creativity and transform this property into your dream home.
